translation.PRIVACY_POLICY_P1: This privacy policy applies to the Corny app (hereinafter referred to as the 'App') created by Corny (hereinafter referred to as the 'Service Provider') for mobile devices and is provided as a free service. This service is designed to be used as-is.
translation.PRIVACY_POLICY_DATE: This privacy policy is effective as of November 2, 2024.

translation.PRIVACY_POLICY_L2: The pages you visit in the App, the date and time of your visit, the time spent on these pages

translation.PRIVACY_POLICY_P3: The App collects your device's location, which helps the Service Provider determine your approximate geographic location and is used in the following ways:
translation.PRIVACY_POLICY_L5: Location-Based Services: The Service Provider uses location data to provide features such as personalized content, relevant recommendations, and location-based services.
translation.PRIVACY_POLICY_L6: Analytics and Improvements: Aggregated and anonymized location data helps the Service Provider analyze user behavior, identify trends, and improve the overall performance and functionality of the App.
translation.PRIVACY_POLICY_L7: Third-Party Services: The Service Provider may periodically share anonymized location data with third-party services that assist in improving and optimizing the App.
translation.PRIVACY_POLICY_P4: The Service Provider may use the information you provide to communicate with you from time to time to provide important updates, necessary notifications, and marketing promotions.
translation.PRIVACY_POLICY_P5: To provide a better experience, the Service Provider may request certain personally identifiable information from you while using the App. The information requested will be stored and used as described in this privacy policy.
translation.PRIVACY_POLICY_P6: The Service Provider may periodically share only aggregated, anonymized data with third-party services that help improve the App and its services. The Service Provider may share your information with third parties as described in this privacy notice.
translation.PRIVACY_POLICY_P7: The App uses third-party services that have their own Privacy Policies for processing data. Below are the links to the Privacy Policies of third-party service providers used by the App:

translation.PRIVACY_POLICY_L9: When they believe in good faith that disclosure is necessary to protect their rights, ensure your or others' safety, investigate fraud, or respond to a government request;
